description: TRUEALPHA RiverNorth Enhanced Pre-Merger SPAC ETF (SPCZ) is an actively managed fund that invests in pre-merger securities of special purpose acquisition companies (SPACs). Also known as 'blank check companies', their business plan is to raise capital in an Initial Public Offering (IPO) and, within a specific period of time, engage in a merger or acquisition with one or more unidentified companies.
name: RIVERNORTH ENHANCED PRE-MERGER SPAC ETF
